" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 595px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Cervical length in a curved cervix",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 575px; height: 435px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Evaluation of cervical length in a patient with a curved cervix. If the widest distance (A, red arrow) between the yellow lines is greater than 5 mm, use the sum of B and C as the best measurement of cervical length. If less than or equal to 5 mm, use D as the best measurement of cervical length.",
